data.description: Beautiful Full Brick home on a spacious and private, fenced lot.  Hardwood floors in formal Dining room and Foyer.  Den features gas fireplace, carpet, custom built-in bookshelf and a door to the large sun porch.  Kitchen features granite counter tops, pecan colored cabinets, center island, eat in area and door to the large sun porch.  Stairs in kitchen lead to large bonus room with custom built-in cabinets.  Primary suite features vaulted ceiling, dual sinks, tub and separate shower.  Beautiful sun porch and deck overlook the backyard and is great for entertaining.  Backyard is fenced in and private.  Come see this beautiful home and neighborhood located close to UNCC, I-485, I-85, I-77, light rail, Concord Mills, community access to The Mallard Creek Greenway and so much more!
